================================================================================\
APP DESCRIPTION\
================================================================================\
\
PriceMatch AI is an AI-powered fashion discovery and shopping assistant iOS app. Users take photos of clothing, shoes, or accessories, and the app uses Google Gemini Vision AI to identify the item and find similar or cheaper alternatives from major retailers. The app includes personalized style recommendations, an AI fashion chatbot, and gamification features to increase engagement.\
\
